title: The New Tsars 03 - The Madmen of Baku (2006) (Scanlation) cbr
description:
The edges of Russia's southern borders : Yuri Vladimir finds himself demoted and assigned to Baku, capital of the Republic of Azerbaijan.
A Canadian oil company takes advantage of the president's greed to expand its empire.
Gunther, a mysterious man in the employ of an Arab state, seeks to overthrow the corrupt power of Baku in order to establish an Islamic republic.
More disillusioned than ever, Yuri is at the heart of this chess game that is played on the explosive shores of the Caspian Sea.

enjoy
